"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-04-23-andrea-spendolini-sirieix-telling-stories-amazing-olympic-stars-20702769\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"It was great to win ten-metre platform bronze and team silver at the World Cup Super Final in China but it got me thinking.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 94, \"end\": 99, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9432839733996637, \"rank\": 0.05965668494536506, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ten-metre platform bronze and team silver\", \"from\": 20, \"to\": 61}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Cup Super Final\", \"from\": 65, \"to\": 90}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last weekend in Xi'an was another vital step towards thissummer's ParisOlympicsand things are coming along nicely, both for me and the team.\", \"from\": 125, \"to\": 265, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 141, \"end\": 146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xi'an\", \"score\": 0.9999999909550752, \"rank\": 9.044783237684198e-09, \"text\": \"Xi'an\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xi'an\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Xi'an\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another vital step\", \"from\": 151, \"to\": 169}, {\"ngram\": \"thissummer's ParisOlympicsand things\", \"from\": 178, \"to\": 214}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 256, \"to\": 264}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every day I am surrounded by amazing team-mates, athletes who dedicate themselves to their sport.\", \"from\": 267, \"to\": 364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"amazing team-mates\", \"from\": 296, \"to\": 314}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 324}, {\"ngram\": \"their sport\", \"from\": 352, \"to\": 363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But they are also human beings and have great stories to tell, something which I feel we do not hear enough of at times.\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 485, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"human beings\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 395}, {\"ngram\": \"great stories\", \"from\": 405, \"to\": 418}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 437}, {\"ngram\": \"times\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 484}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am passionate about journalism and in September I am going to university to study while I continue to dive so that I can hopefully be one of the people to help tell these stories.\", \"from\": 487, \"to\": 668, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"journalism\", \"from\": 509, \"to\": 519}, {\"ngram\": \"September\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 536}, {\"ngram\": \"university\", \"from\": 551, \"to\": 561}, {\"ngram\": \"the people\", \"from\": 630, \"to\": 640}, {\"ngram\": \"these stories\", \"from\": 654, \"to\": 667}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am aware the prism I see sport through is diving.\", \"from\": 670, \"to\": 721, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the prism\", \"from\": 681, \"to\": 690}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 697, \"to\": 702}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's all-consuming and in many ways has been all I have known sport-wise from a very young age.\", \"from\": 722, \"to\": 817, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"many ways\", \"from\": 748, \"to\": 757}, {\"ngram\": \"a very young age\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I need to have a greater knowledge across a wider range of sports and am trying to get just that, having met with some of our swimmers, watched them train and discovered how complex their sport is.\", \"from\": 819, \"to\": 1019, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a greater knowledge\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 856}, {\"ngram\": \"a wider range\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 877}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 887}, {\"ngram\": \"our swimmers\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 956}, {\"ngram\": \"their sport\", \"from\": 1004, \"to\": 1015}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I also spoke to Tokyo Olympic silver medallist Emily Campbell about weightlifting and it brought home how limited to just one sport I have been so far.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1172, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1037, \"end\": 1042, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9957905578490883, \"rank\": 0.004163087410402146, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1068, \"end\": 1082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Campbell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Emily Campbell\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Campbell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emily_Campbell\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just one sport\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I intend to make new friends and meet many more from other sports as I go along.\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1254, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"new friends\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1202}, {\"ngram\": \"other sports\", \"from\": 1227, \"to\": 1239}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Journalism has always interested in me and I really want to be able to use that as a way of getting over athletes' back stories.\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1383, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Journalism\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1265}, {\"ngram\": \"a way\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1343}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes' back stories\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At a certain point, I knew I wanted to do a degree or take a career in something that was as far away from sport as possible.\", \"from\": 1385, \"to\": 1510, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a certain point\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1403}, {\"ngram\": \"a degree\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1435}, {\"ngram\": \"a career\", \"from\": 1444, \"to\": 1452}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 1456, \"to\": 1465}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I like writing and I like to talk, and hopefully I can also understand people's viewpoints.\", \"from\": 1511, \"to\": 1602, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people's viewpoints\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1601}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A lot of time as an athlete is spent in your own bubble.\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1660, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lot\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1609}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1617}, {\"ngram\": \"an athlete\", \"from\": 1621, \"to\": 1631}, {\"ngram\": \"your own bubble\", \"from\": 1644, \"to\": 1659}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, some people still do not see what we do as a full-time job, despite the incredibly hard work that goes in from athletes, supported by the National Lottery, that is simply not seen by the wider public.\", \"from\": 1661, \"to\": 1870, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1808, \"end\": 1824, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"score\": 0.9999767519676713, \"rank\": 2.3248565233899486e-05, \"text\": \"National Lottery\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some people\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1681}, {\"ngram\": \"a full-time job\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1728}, {\"ngram\": \"the incredibly hard work\", \"from\": 1738, \"to\": 1762}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1789}, {\"ngram\": \"the wider public\", \"from\": 1853, \"to\": 1869}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We represent Great Britain on the biggest stage every four years and it's important for me to get our message across.\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1989, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1885, \"end\": 1898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999838747180108, \"rank\": 8.244096598642696e-06, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the biggest stage\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1919}, {\"ngram\": \"our message\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 1981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am also aware that while it is the dream of lots of young kids to become an Olympian, it also opens doors for us when we finish competing.\", \"from\": 1990, \"to\": 2130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2068, \"end\": 2076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"score\": 0.999999184697222, \"rank\": 8.153032937688491e-07, \"text\": \"Olympian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Olympic_Games\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dream\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2032}, {\"ngram\": \"lots\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2040}, {\"ngram\": \"young kids\", \"from\": 2044, \"to\": 2054}, {\"ngram\": \"doors\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2097}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We do sport but we also enjoy the same things as everyone else - I like chocolate, as maybe you do too!\", \"from\": 2132, \"to\": 2235, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 2138, \"to\": 2143}, {\"ngram\": \"the same things\", \"from\": 2162, \"to\": 2177}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2189}, {\"ngram\": \"chocolate\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2213}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are not different in any way as people, we just focus our lives around our sport.\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2320, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any way\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2267}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2271, \"to\": 2277}, {\"ngram\": \"our lives\", \"from\": 2293, \"to\": 2302}, {\"ngram\": \"our sport\", \"from\": 2310, \"to\": 2319}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For me, aged 19, every day is a learning experience, every camp an education.\", \"from\": 2322, \"to\": 2399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every day\", \"from\": 2339, \"to\": 2348}, {\"ngram\": \"a learning experience\", \"from\": 2352, \"to\": 2373}, {\"ngram\": \"every camp\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2385}, {\"ngram\": \"an education\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2398}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Real life kicks in when your career in the pool finishes, which hopefully will not be any time soon, and I am trying to take as much in as I can from the experiences I am gaining.\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Real life\", \"from\": 2400, \"to\": 2409}, {\"ngram\": \"the pool finishes\", \"from\": 2439, \"to\": 2456}, {\"ngram\": \"any time\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2494}, {\"ngram\": \"the experiences\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have been travelling the world without my parents from a very young age and have immersed myself in cultures across the planet.\", \"from\": 2581, \"to\": 2710, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2613}, {\"ngram\": \"my parents\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2632}, {\"ngram\": \"a very young age\", \"from\": 2638, \"to\": 2654}, {\"ngram\": \"cultures\", \"from\": 2683, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"the planet\", \"from\": 2699, \"to\": 2709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I would not have had anything approaching that unique take on life if it wasn't for diving so I am very grateful for what I have learned, and continue to learn.\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2871, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2732, \"to\": 2740}, {\"ngram\": \"that unique take\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2769}, {\"ngram\": \"diving\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My worth is not dependent on my failures, though.\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2922, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My worth\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2881}, {\"ngram\": \"my failures\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will never be perfect and that's very, very reassuring.\", \"from\": 2923, \"to\": 2980, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am not looking for perfection and my faith in God plays a big part in my life and the perspective I have on my career.\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 3101, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"perfection\", \"from\": 3002, \"to\": 3012}, {\"ngram\": \"my faith\", \"from\": 3017, \"to\": 3025}, {\"ngram\": \"God\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3032}, {\"ngram\": \"a big part\", \"from\": 3039, \"to\": 3049}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 3053, \"to\": 3060}, {\"ngram\": \"the perspective\", \"from\": 3065, \"to\": 3080}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 3091, \"to\": 3100}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Chinese, who I aspire to and am chasing down for gold medals at the Games, are also not perfect.\", \"from\": 3103, \"to\": 3203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3107, \"end\": 3114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9957346839915886, \"rank\": 0.003710509085492059, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"gold medals\", \"from\": 3156, \"to\": 3167}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3180}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The ten mark does not mean perfection, it just means excellent.\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3267, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The ten mark\", \"from\": 3204, \"to\": 3216}, {\"ngram\": \"perfection\", \"from\": 3231, \"to\": 3241}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So with less than 100 days to go until Paris, I feel content I know who I am and where I am going, within the greater context of my life.\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3308, \"end\": 3313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999939484604354, \"rank\": 6.051576210503965e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"less than 100 days\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3295}, {\"ngram\": \"the greater context\", \"from\": 3375, \"to\": 3394}, {\"ngram\": \"my life\", \"from\": 3398, \"to\": 3405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The more I get to know about other athletes and their sports, and find out about people's lives, the more I learn and grow and that's so important as I want to be able to tell people's stories about who they are away from sport.\", \"from\": 3408, \"to\": 3636, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other athletes\", \"from\": 3437, \"to\": 3451}, {\"ngram\": \"their sports\", \"from\": 3456, \"to\": 3468}, {\"ngram\": \"people's lives\", \"from\": 3489, \"to\": 3503}, {\"ngram\": \"people's stories\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3600}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3630, \"to\": 3635}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are all just normal people after all, medals or not.\", \"from\": 3637, \"to\": 3692, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just normal people\", \"from\": 3648, \"to\": 3666}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 3678, \"to\": 3684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"National Lottery players raise more than \\u00a330m a week for good causes including vital funding into sport, from grassroots to elite.\", \"from\": 3694, \"to\": 3824, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3694, \"end\": 3710, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"score\": 0.9999767519676713, \"rank\": 2.3248565233899486e-05, \"text\": \"National Lottery\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Lottery_Heritage_Fund\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more than \\u00a330m\", \"from\": 3725, \"to\": 3739}, {\"ngram\": \"good causes\", \"from\": 3751, \"to\": 3762}, {\"ngram\": \"vital funding\", \"from\": 3773, \"to\": 3786}, {\"ngram\": \"sport\", \"from\": 3792, \"to\": 3797}, {\"ngram\": \"grassroots\", \"from\": 3804, \"to\": 3814}, {\"ngram\": \"elite\", \"from\": 3818, \"to\": 3823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To find out more, visithttp://www.lotterygoodcauses.org.uk#TNLAthletes ArrowMORE:I am looking forward to retiring but not before beating the Chinese to Olympic gold in Paris ArrowMORE:Finding your sporting community is like kryptonite to loneliness ArrowMORE:Shove affairs and heated rivalries can push women's game forward Get your favourite puzzles when they are ready to play on the website sent directly to you every day and track your daily streak!\", \"from\": 3825, \"to\": 4282, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3967, \"end\": 3974, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"score\": 0.9957346839915886, \"rank\": 0.003710509085492059, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chinese_language\"}, {\"begin\": 3994, \"end\": 3999, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999939484604354, \"rank\": 6.051576210503965e-06, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ArrowMORE\", \"from\": 3896, \"to\": 3905}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold\", \"from\": 3977, \"to\": 3989}, {\"ngram\": \"your sporting community\", \"from\": 4017, \"to\": 4040}, {\"ngram\": \"kryptonite\", \"from\": 4049, \"to\": 4059}, {\"ngram\": \"ArrowMORE\", \"from\": 4074, \"to\": 4083}, {\"ngram\": \"Shove affairs\", \"from\": 4084, \"to\": 4097}, {\"ngram\": \"heated rivalries\", \"from\": 4102, \"to\": 4118}, {\"ngram\": \"women's game\", \"from\": 4128, \"to\": 4140}, {\"ngram\": \"your favourite puzzles\", \"from\": 4153, \"to\": 4175}, {\"ngram\": \"the website\", \"from\": 4207, \"to\": 4218}, {\"ngram\": \"your daily streak\", \"from\": 4260, \"to\": 4277}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This site is protected by reCAPTCHA and theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms of Serviceapply.\", \"from\": 4284, \"to\": 4373, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This site\", \"from\": 4284, \"to\": 4293}, {\"ngram\": \"reCAPTCHA\", \"from\": 4310, \"to\": 4319}, {\"ngram\": \"theGoogle Privacy PolicyandTerms\", \"from\": 4324, \"to\": 4356}, {\"ngram\": \"Serviceapply\", \"from\": 4360, \"to\": 4372}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your information will be used in line with ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 4374, \"to\": 4434, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your information\", \"from\": 4374, \"to\": 4390}, {\"ngram\": \"line\", \"from\": 4407, \"to\": 4411}, {\"ngram\": \"ourPrivacy Policy\", \"from\": 4417, \"to\": 4434}]}]}"